{
  "info": {
    "name": "CCS Profiling API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for CCS Profiling System with authentication and all modules.\n\n## Quick Start\n1. Set the {{base_url}} variable to your server URL (default: http://localhost:3000)\n2. Run the 'Login' request to authenticate\n3. Access token is automatically saved and used for all subsequent requests\n\n## Environment Variables\n- base_url: http://localhost:3000 (local) or your production URL\n- token: Auto-populated after login\n- refreshToken: Auto-populated after login\n\n## Authentication\nAll admin endpoints require Bearer token authentication. Login first to get your token.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "refreshToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Automatically add Authorization header for authenticated requests",
          "const token = pm.collectionVariables.get('token');",
          "if (token) {",
          "    pm.request.headers.add({",
          "        key: 'Authorization',",
          "        value: `Bearer ${token}`",
          "    });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health Check",
      "description": "System health check endpoint - No authentication required",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Check if the API server is running and healthy. Returns server status, timestamp, and environment."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Authentication endpoints - JWT-based authentication with access and refresh tokens",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (response.success && response.data.tokens) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('token', response.data.tokens.access.token);",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', response.data.tokens.refresh.token);",
                  "        console.log('Access token saved to collection variables');",
                  "        console.log('Token expires at:', response.data.tokens.access.expiresAt);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@ccs.edu\",\n  \"password\": \"pass1234\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login with email and password. Returns nested token structure with access and refresh tokens including expiration times. Rate limited to 5 requests per 15 minutes.\n\nResponse format:\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"user\": { \"id\": \"...\", \"email\": \"...\", \"role\": \"...\" },\n    \"tokens\": {\n      \"access\": { \"token\": \"...\", \"expiresAt\": \"...\" },\n      \"refresh\": { \"token\": \"...\", \"expiresAt\": \"...\" }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Current User (Me)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/me",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Get current authenticated user information. Requires valid access token."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (response.success && response.data.tokens) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('token', response.data.tokens.access.token);",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', response.data.tokens.refresh.token);",
                  "        console.log('Tokens refreshed and saved to collection variables');",
                  "        console.log('New token expires at:', response.data.tokens.access.expiresAt);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/refresh",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "refresh"]
            },
            "description": "Refresh access token using refresh token. Returns new access and refresh tokens with expiration times. Rate limited to 5 requests per 15 minutes.\n\nResponse format:\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"tokens\": {\n      \"access\": { \"token\": \"...\", \"expiresAt\": \"...\" },\n      \"refresh\": { \"token\": \"...\", \"expiresAt\": \"...\" }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Change Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"oldPassword\": \"pass1234\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"newPassword456\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/change-password",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "change-password"]
            },
            "description": "Change password for authenticated user. Requires valid access token and correct old password."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "Logout endpoint. Currently returns success message. Token invalidation handled client-side."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
